item.description: I walked past Melbourne University’s Grainger Museum, which is dedicated to the Australian composer Percy Grainger. Kudos to the Wiggles for adapting one of his compositions into a children’s song.
First time on Melbourne train since the pandemic!! I hadn’t seen this view since the middle of March.
